content:
The new Einstein Studio tab in Data Cloud is now your home base for creating and connecting your AI models. We replaced the Legacy tab with one experience that provides access to more enhanced AI capabilities, such as predictive and generative AI models and activity metrics. You also get data, model, and training alerts.

This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions. The functionality is available starting in July 2024.
title: Einstein Studio Legacy Tab Retirement in Data Cloud
